name: Kelvin Raffael Stinghen
body:
Hi! Thank you for being at here! :smiley:

My name is Kelvin Stinghen, and I'm an enthusiast developer from Brazil. Currently residing at Blumenau, SC, but born in the litlle village of Massaranduba, SC.

I'm addicted with ruby development (web and client), and, more and more, I like to be part of this pretty awesome community. But, I have profissional experiences with Java, C, Delphi, HTML, JavaScript and CSS.
